Disc Ability Score Description

Disc 08 Trace 6 When it enters a battle, the Pokémon copies an opposing Pokémon's Ability.

Disc 23 Frostproof 6 The Pokémon resists Ice-type moves and cannot be frostbitten.
Disc 24 Levitate 8 By floating in the air, the Pokémon receives full immunity to all Ground-type moves.
